    },
    {
      "segment_id": "call1_S14",
      "text": "Okay. Lal Chand ji, according to the proposal, we will do a video medical verification. Along with the verification, some medical history questions will also be asked. The information and answers you provide on this call will be related to health and habits and will become part of the insurance application.",
