    {
      "segment_id": "call1_S15",
      "text": "Upon acceptance of the proposal, a legal contract can be formed between Tata AIA Life Insurance and you. If there is any incorrect or false statement, it will impact the policy; the policy can be canceled, and the claim can be rejected. Therefore, you are requested to think and answer correctly whatever you answer. This call is being recorded for quality purposes, okay?",
